text.text: It was an intensive exposure to python programming language and involved use of PyCharm, Google Colab, Jupyter Notebook and Anaconda Spyder. It involved a thorugh coverage of fundamentals of Python programming language.

text.headline: Python - Data Warehouse & Predictive Analysys
text.text: Another really heavy weight course in data warehousing and predictive analysis using python. Again it involved heavy use of tools: PyCharm, Google Colab, Jupyter Notebook and Anaconda Spyder

text.headline: Python - AI for Software Developers
text.text: Another really challanging course that covered different facets of Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning using Python. Again it involved heavy use of tools: PyCharm, Streamlit, Google Colab, Jupyter Notebook and Anaconda Spyder
